data.description: Move in Ready!  This 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home is situated in the highly sought-after community of Copper Mill. As you step into the welcoming front foyer, a beautiful formal dining room awaits on your left, adorned with rustic wooden beams, contemporary lighting fixtures, and raised ceilings.  Directly ahead, the living room beckons with its built-in features, a gas fireplace, and a custom mantel accented by granite. To the left of the foyer, is well equipped kitchen, boasting a gas cooktop, pristine white cabinetry, granite countertops, a breakfast island, built-in microwave, wall oven, and a generously sized walk-in pantry.  On this side of the house, additional spaces include a versatile BONUS/OFFICE and a laundry room with ample cabinetry, providing convenient access to the garage. The master suite is tucked away towards the rear of the residence, offering a spacious bedroom and an en-suite bathroom complete with dual vanities, granite surfaces, a luxurious garden soaking tub, a separate shower, and an expansive walk-in closet.  The three spacious guest bedrooms are thoughtfully positioned on the right side of the home and are complemented by a full guest bathroom. The interior of the home is graced by updated color schemes, contemporary lighting fixtures, exposed wooden beams, meticulously crafted engineered hardwood flooring, and ceramic tile in the wet areas.  Outside, the property boasts landscaping and a fully fenced yard. The community itself offers a private clubhouse, a swimming pool, a playful splash pad, two tennis courts, and a charming neighborhood picnic area complete with a playground.  This amazing home is located minutes from shopping, dining, local schools and entertainment.  It is also a quick drive to downtown Baton Rouge, LSU and the Baton Rouge airport.  Schedule your showing today to see what this home has to offer!
